pages(interface=OnboardingPageData).title: What is QuickStart Flutter?
pages(interface=OnboardingPageData).message: QuickStart Flutter is a project to speed up the bootstrapping of new Flutter projects. It already comes with a series of features ready to use, such as internationalization, themes, routes, state management, among others.

pages(interface=OnboardingPageData).title: Let's get started?
pages(interface=OnboardingPageData).message: Ready to explore everything QuickStart Flutter has to offer? Let's get started!
